headline: These Stocks Moved the Most Today: Apple, Tesla, DJT, Informatica, Super Micro, PDD, SoundHound, and More

headline: SMCI Stock Is Set to Snap a 5-Day Losing Streak. Super Micro Is Soaring—for Now.
summary: Super Micro Computer  stock powered higher in Tuesday trading, tracking to snap a five-day losing streak.  Shares of the server maker have been particularly volatile since the start of 2024, when they exploded on the artificial-intelligence boom.  Shares wavered earlier this year as investors waited to see whether the company would avoid removal from the index.
